Titolo: NBA Live 15

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: NBA Live 15 is a basketball simulation video game for the PlayStation 4 and Xbox One released on October 28, 2014, in North America and on October 31, 2014, in Europe. It features Damian Lillard of the Portland Trail Blazers as its cover athlete. The release date was moved due to EA Sports wanting to polish the title before release. This is the second installment of the game after taking a four-year hiatus starting in 2010.
NBA Live 15 was followed by NBA Live 16.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: 56
